Package: Rminibwa
Title: R Interface and Runtime Dispatch Experiments for 'minibwa'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Sounkou Mahamane", family = "Toure",
      email = "sounkoutoure@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person(given = "Dana-Farber Cancer Institute", role = "cph",
      comment = "Copyright holder of upstream minibwa, when vendored or linked")
  )
Description: Provides an R-facing home for experiments around the 'minibwa'
    short-read aligner. The initial package exposes small wrappers around the
    'minibwa' command line interface while documenting the intended native C API
    and 'SIMDe'-backed runtime Single Instruction Multiple Data ('SIMD')
    dispatch shape for a future library-backed implementation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
SystemRequirements: GNU make, zlib
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    RsimdDispatch,
    roxygen2,
    tinytest
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
URL: https://github.com/sounkou-bioinfo/Rminibwa
BugReports: https://github.com/sounkou-bioinfo/Rminibwa/issues
